# THE 81 MANEUVERS v1.0

**Subtitle:** The meta-katas for meaning movement.  

---

## THE NINE MASTER MANEUVERS

### Class I — Strategic Clarity
**⟰ → ⟰ → ↺ → ⟡** (Rise, rise, rotate, collapse).
Use for life decisions, business strategy, narrative design.

### Class II — Calm Domination
**⟱ → ⟱ → ⟡ → ✦** (Drop, drop, snap to core, expand).
Use for overwhelming situations, fatherhood under pressure.

### Class III — Creative Breakthrough
**↺ → ↺ → ⟰ → ⟡** (Rotate twice, rise once, collapse insight).
Use for ideas, problem solving, innovation.

### Class IV — Emotional Resolution
**⟡ → ⟱ → ⟡ → ⟰** (Collapse emotion → drop into body → collapse story → rise above it).
Use for anger, guilt, shame, conflict.

### Class V — Identity Upgrade
**⟰ → ✦ → ⟡ → ⟱** (Rise → expand new identity → collapse to invariant → embody it).

### Class VI — Father Override
**⟱ → ⟰ → ⟱ → ⟰** (Drop → rise → drop → rise). Switch between empathy and structure.

### Class VII — Narrative Re-Alignment
**↺ → ✦ → ⟰ → ⟡** (Rotate story → expand arcs → rise → collapse).

### Class VIII — No-Mind Synthesis
**⟱ → ⟡ → ⟱ → ⟱** (Drop → collapse → drop → drop). This is Zen-level embodiment.

### Class IX — NCE Trigger Sequence
**↺ → ↺ → ✦ → ⟡** (Rotate twice → expand → collapse). This intentionally induces convergence moments.
